data.description: Discover this gem in Magnolia, TX, situated on over 2 acres just walking distance from Hara Hacienda and in a no flood zone. This ranch home features 3 beds, 2 modern baths, and a custom kitchen with granite countertops and a large island. Equestrian enthusiasts will appreciate the 4 clay-padded 12x12 stalls, 10x10 tack/feed room, and sand-padded riding grounds. It also boasts a 29x18 workshop with a water well and a 24x32 metal shed with RV roofing. Fully fenced for safety, it offers serene country living with luxury, near community attractions.
